HEROINE

Why do you want to fall in love with me?

LION

Warrior princesses are the highest form of life.

HEROINE

Some humans would say lions are the highest form of life.  If you fall
in love with a lion, she'll hunt food.

LION

I'm a military commander lion.  I see you in my eyes and your pose in my
pose.  All other heroines are mere mortals.

HEROINE

Ever wait in long security lines, get full body scans, sit in
overcrowded steel tubes, and survive on peanuts for hours at a time,
waiting for a light to turn on to use the restroom?

LION

What does that have to do with loving a warrior princess?

HEROINE

It's a large part of the life of a warrior princess.

LION

Because we live in the baby boomer nation and I can only run 100 feet, I
get a huge thrill out of running into someone with hair, who can run 1.5
miles.











